    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚任职时间最长的央行行长获得新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-mandate-in-romania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚央行行长穆古尔·伊萨雷斯库 (Mugur Isarescu) 获得议会批准，延长其五年任期，成为世界上任职时间最长的央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-mandate-in-romania</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:51:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗计划五年内每年盈利 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/apollo-projects-10-billion-of-annual-earnings-in-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 预计，到 2029 年，其资产管理和退休业务的年收益将达到 100 亿美元，这得益于投资者对私人信贷和年金的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/apollo-projects-10-billion-of-annual-earnings-in-five-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行获得 42 亿美元 AT1 债券交易订单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/commerzbank-to-sell-loss-absorbing-at1s-as-unicredit-circles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 表示有意收购德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 以来，该银行首次公开​​进军债券市场，收到了超过 42 亿美元的额外一级债券销售订单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/commerzbank-to-sell-loss-absorbing-at1s-as-unicredit-circles</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有迹象显示伊朗准备袭击以色列，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明伊朗正准备对以色列发动导弹袭击，这将扩大中东冲突并可能增加原油供应中断的可能性，导致油价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球债务狂潮带来创纪录的 6000 亿美元债券销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/borrowers-smash-global-records-to-sell-600-billion-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一个月，全球各地的企业和政府纷纷涌入债券市场，抓住美国总统大选前利率下降的机会，许多人担心大选将引发市场动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/borrowers-smash-global-records-to-sell-600-billion-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
